This triple feature is the perfect trio of movies for any occasion, babysitting, girls night in, or just in the mood for a feel-good story. Whether you are 4 or 84, you will find joy in these three new takes on a timeless classic. Each movie is unique in their own way and has you rooting for Cinderella from the very start to the end when she finds her Prince Charming.

The three stories may be based around the classic Cinderella tale, but they are in no way the same story. In these three movies the Cinderellas are all raised by an evil step mother with evil step siblings, but instead of Prince Charming saving them, they save themselves. They show that their hard work can take them anywhere they want to go, and any Prince Charming along the way is there to support them on their journey. These three movies inspire you to be all you can be despite everything that is trying to hold you back.

The three DVDs are durable and hold up well after continuous use. Like any other DVD you have to be aware of the possibilities of scratches but if you take care of them, these DVDs can bring you joy for years to come. All the delight that these movies bring over shadows any of the down falls that you might find in the product, such as one DVD holder in the case for all three DVDs. Although these movies are not in HD they still have a very high- quality imaging.

One of the best parts about this product is that it is three DVDs for half the price of one DVD at the store. The extra money you save from this purchase leaves you with more money to spend on snacks and comfortable clothes for a movie night. The PG rating makes all three movies family friendly, so everyone can watch and enjoy a night in filled with snacks and fun.

In comparison to other purchases made on amazon, this is one of the most fulfilling. It hits all the major components to be a worthwhile purchase. It was affordable, and the fact that there were three products for even less than the price of one produces a euphoric feeling. The durability of the DVDs appeals to those who like their purchases to stand the test of time. The last reason this purchase stands out compared to others is the empowering and feel good emotions it takes the watcher through. A timeless classic, reinvented in three different ways, is the perfect purchase for someone in need of a mood booster.
